
## Installation
```bash
# requirements: node 16
cd /web
npm install
cd ..
cd /server
npm install
```

## Running locally
```bash
# from root directory
bash run-dev.sh
```
Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) to view it in the browser.

## Running in docker (build locally)
```bash
bash run-docker-dev.sh
```
Open [http://localhost:8010](http://localhost:8010) to view it in the browser.

## Running in docker
```bash
bash run-docker.sh   
``` 


